key_94.name: Grateful Dead
set1:
Reckoning Mix:

Dire Wolf
The Race is On 
Oh Babe It Ain't No Lie 
It Must Have Been the Roses 
Dark Hollow 
China Doll 
I've Been All Around this World 
Monkey and the Engineer 
Jackaroe 
Deep Elem Blues 
Cassidy 
To Lay Me Down 
Rosalie McFall 
On the Road Again 
Birdsong 
Ripple
key_94.comment:
Notes: This tape is purportedly the GD's Club Front mix that 
was submitted to Arista for the Reckoning LP in 1981. Noticeable 
differences are mainly the presence of more audience between 
some songs, and the mix is a bit different from the final LP. 
Fifteen tracks were released on a single CD in 1988 (with OBIANL 
omitted), then remastered again and expanded for the 2006 double 
CD reissue. This sounds quite different from the CD versions
